Connie Needham https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Connie_Needham 0 Connie Needham (born December 5, 1959) is an American actress and dance instructor. As Connie Newton, she portrayed Elizabeth Bradford on the television series Eight is Enough from 1977 to 1981. Connie_Needham ( born December_5_,_1959 ) is an_American_actress_and_dance_instructor .
